summary.description:
Today, a bit warmer for the feels like temperature (up 3.1°C) and outside temperature (up 2.2°C), more moisture-laden outside humidity (up 13%), and drier conditions in rainfall (down 0.3 mm).

Compared to today, yesterday also had noticeable differences in rainfall (up 0.3 mm) and cloud levels (up 1066 m).

The past week and month had observable variation in cloud levels (up 1178 m), feels like temperature (up 2.7°C), outside temperature (up 1.9°C), and inside temperature (up 1.8°C) when compared to today.
